      STR_EXTERNAL_EQUIPMENT_ACQUISITION: "External Equipment Acquisition"
      STR_EXTERNAL_EQUIPMENT_ACQUISITION_UFOPEDIA: "The various governments and corporations member of the Council of Funding States provide standardized equipment. Still, if XCOM considers it necessary, we could peek around in the global arms trade. Military markets all over the world could sell us their assets, after opening a regional commercial channel. Take in consideration, though: regions with larger industrial outputs (this is, more weapons available at once) may take longer to contact, due the higher demand. If the providing  country leaves the XCOM initiative, it will stop selling us their items until their return."
